 Continues Pre-Production and is Still Aiming to Begin Production in June|accessdate=March 26, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326204324/https://thedisinsider.com/2020/03/26/doctor-strange-sequel-continues-pre-production-and-is-still-aiming-to-begin-production-in-june/|archive-date=March 26, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Jurassic World: Dominion]]''<ref name=\"UniversalProductionSuspensions\" />\n*''[[King Richard (film)|King Richard]]''<ref name=\"DeadlineFB3\" />\n*''[[The Last Duel (2020 film)|The Last Duel]]''<ref name=\"HollywoodReporter\" />\n*''[[Macbeth (upcoming film)|Macbeth]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/denzel-washington-macbeth-movie-hiatus-coronavirus-1202893688/|title=Denzel Washington, Frances McDormand, Joel Coen A24 'Macbeth' Movie On Hiatus|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|date=March 26, 2020|accessdate=April 7, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401201427/https://deadline.com/2020/03/denzel-washington-macbeth-movie-hiatus-coronavirus-1202893688/|archive-date=April 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[The Matrix 4]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/the-matrix-4-coronavirus-production-stop-1202884580/|title='The Matrix 4' Production Pauses In Berlin Amid Coronavirus Climate|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|date=March 16, 2020|access-date=March 16, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316180056/https://deadline.com/2020/03/the-matrix-4-coronavirus-production-stop-1202884580/|archive-date=March 16, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Midnight in the Switchgrass]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/midnight-in-the-switchgrass-postpone-coronavirus-puerto-rico-shoot-megan-fox-emile-hirsch-bruce-willis-machine-gun-kelly-randall-emmett-1202884454/|title=Indie 'Midnight In The Switchgrass' Postpones Puerto Rico Shoot Over Coronavirus Scare|first1=Mike Fleming|last1=Jr|first2=Mike Flemi