riety\" />\n|-\n|''Our Ladies'' || {{dts|April 24, 2020}} || {{dts|September 11, 2020}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.empirecinemas.co.uk/synopsis/our_ladies/f7076|title=Our Ladies|website=[[Empire Cinemas]]|accessdate=17 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317175332/https://www.empirecinemas.co.uk/synopsis/our_ladies/f7076|archive-date=March 17, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[The Personal History of David Copperfield]]'' || {{dts|May 8, 2020}} || TBA (outside the United Kingdom)<ref name=\"HWRMulan\" />\n|-\n|''[[Peter Rabbit 2: The Runaway]]'' || {{dts|April 3, 2020}} || {{dts|January  15, 2021}}<ref name=\"2021Date\" />\n|-\n|''[[Pretty Cure All Stars|Pretty Cure Miracle Leap: A Wonderful Day with Everyone]]'' || {{dts|March 20, 2020}} || {{dts|May 16, 2020}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Spring 2020 Precure Anime Film Delayed Due to Coronavirus COVID-19 Concerns |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-13/spring-2020-precure-anime-film-delayed-due-to-coronavirus-covid-19-concerns/.157496 |website=[[Anime News Network]] |accessdate=March 13, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320133524/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-13/spring-2020-precure-anime-film-delayed-due-to-coronavirus-covid-19-concerns/.157496 |archive-date=March 20, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Precure Miracle Leap Anime Film Opens on May 16 |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-20/precure-miracle-leap-anime-film-opens-on-may-16/.157720 |website=[[Anime News Network]] |accessdate=March 20, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320110448/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-20/precure-miracle-leap-anime-film-opens-on-may-16/.157720 |archive-date=March 20, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Princess Principal]]'' || {{dts|April 10, 2020}} || TBA<ref>{{cite web |title=1st Princess Principal Sequel Anime Film Delayed Due to COVID-19 Coronavirus Concerns |url=https://www.animenewsnetwor