 pushed back. The new release date is to be announced. | url = https://kotaku.com/the-sonic-the-hedgehog-movie-was-originally-scheduled-t-1842146174 | work = [[Kotaku]] | location = | access-date = March 16, 2020 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321010612/https://kotaku.com/the-sonic-the-hedgehog-movie-was-originally-scheduled-t-1842146174 | archive-date = March 21, 2020 | url-status = live}}</ref> until further notice\n|-\n|''[[Sooryavanshi]]'' || {{dts|March 24, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"ABPLive\" />\n|-\n|''[[Soul (2020 film)|Soul]]'' || {{dts|June 19, 2020}} || {{dts|November 20, 2020}}<ref name=\"SoulNovember\" />\n|-\n|''[[Spiral (2020 film)|Spiral]]'' || {{dts|May 15, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"Spiral\" />\n|-\n|''[[The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge on the Run]]'' || {{dts|May 22, 2020}} || {{dts|July 31, 2020}}<ref name=\"ParamountChanges\" />\n|-\n|''[[Stand by Me Doraemon 2]]'' || {{dts|August 7, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"Doremon2\" />\n|-\n|''[[Thor: Love and Thunder]]'' || {{dts|November 5, 2021}} || {{dts|February 18, 2022}}<ref name=\"HollywoodNewDisney\" />{{efn|As part of the future MCU, the initial delay of ''Black Widow'' forced ''Love and Thunder'' to be pushed back, too.}}\n|-\n|''[[The Tomorrow War]]'' || {{dts|December 25, 2020}} || TBA<ref name=\"ParamountChanges\" />\n|-\n|''[[Top Gun: Maverick]]'' || {{dts|June 26, 2020}} || {{dts|December 23, 2020}}<ref name=\"ParamountChanges\" />\n|-\n|''[[Ultraman Taiga The Movie]]'' || {{dts|March 6, 2020}} || TBA<ref>{{cite web |title=TAAF 2020 Event Cancels All Programs, Ultraman Taiga Film Delayed, Namjatown Amusement Park Temporarily Closes |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-02/taaf-2020-event-cancels-all-programs-ultraman-taiga-film-delayed-namjatown-amusement-park-temporarily-closes/.156996 |website=[[Anime News Network]] |accessdate=March 2, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302111500/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-02/taaf-2020-event-cancels-a